OL,3,CFears poorest families won't be able
OL,4,Cto use free childcare proposal
OL,6,FJersey's poorest families may be
OL,7,Funable to benefit from a new
OL,8,Fgovernment proposal to fund 15 hours
OL,9,Fof childcare per week for children
OL,10,Faged two to three.
OL,12,FThe proposal comes in addition to the
OL,13,Fgovernment's current offer of 30 hours
OL,14,Fof free childcare for children aged
OL,15,Fbetween three and four years old.
OL,17,FHowever, not all nurseries have agreed
OL,18,Fto the new proposal, so the government
OL,19,Fcannot pay these institutions directly.
