OL,3,CFears poorest families won't be able
OL,4,Cto use free childcare proposal
OL,6,FInstead, the States have suggested
OL,7,Fpaying nursery fees directly to
OL,8,Fparents in arrears.
OL,10,FThis system may potentially create
OL,11,Fissues for parents who are unable to
OL,12,Fpay the fees upfront, even if it is
OL,13,Freimbursed at the end of each term.
OL,15,FOne parent of a two-year-old child
OL,16,Ftold ITV News: "I probably won't be
OL,17,Fable to make use of it because I don't
OL,18,Fhave the funds for childcare in the
OL,19,Ffirst place.
