OL,3,CFears poorest families won't be able
OL,4,Cto use free childcare proposal
OL,6,F"If I could have access to 15 hours of
OL,7,Ffree childcare, then it would make my
OL,8,Flife as a parent doing everything on
OL,9,Fmy own much easier.
OL,11,F"But the proposal of 15 hours of free
OL,12,Fchildcare isn't that much - I can't go
OL,13,Fback into the workforce until my child
OL,14,Fis older, and I can have 30 hours of
OL,15,Ffree childcare".
OL,17,FMeanwhile, one grandparent supportive
OL,18,Fof the measure told ITV News: "Any
OL,19,Fhelp financially for young families at
OL,20,Fthe moment is definitely a benefit".
