OL,3,CFears poorest families won't be able
OL,4,Cto use free childcare proposal
OL,6,FThe government is proposing to
OL,7,Fcontribute a base rate of #11 per hour
OL,8,Ffor childcare. Alongside the 15 hours
OL,9,Fof childcare per week, this would
OL,10,Ftotal around #2,000 per term.
OL,12,FDeputy Rob Ward, Minister for
OL,13,FEducation and Lifelong Learning, says
OL,14,Ffamilies who are unable to front such
OL,15,Fcosts may be able to access external
OL,16,Fsupport.
OL,18,FHe said: "I don't think this is a huge
OL,19,Fproblem across the island - there are
OL,20,Flots of organisations ready to step in
OL,21,Fand help.
