OL,3,CFears poorest families won't be able
OL,4,Cto use free childcare proposal
OL,6,F"Either charities or parishes can step
OL,7,Fin and help out with the advance
OL,8,Fpayments, with a view to receiving
OL,9,Fthat advance payment back".
OL,11,FHe adds that more than 80% of parents
OL,12,Falready have children in nursery
OL,13,Fplaces.
OL,15,FA decision will be made on whether to
OL,16,Finclude the proposal in the budget at
OL,17,Fthe States Assembly in December.
